  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 180°C.",
    "Season oxtail pieces with salt and pepper.",
    "Coat each piece in breadcrumbs until fully covered.",
    "Heat olive oil in an oven‑safe skillet over medium‑high heat and sear oxtail until golden brown.",
    "Transfer skillet to the oven and roast for 45 minutes.",
    "Dice onion, carrot, mince garlic and ginger.",
    "Remove skillet from oven and add the vegetables; sauté until softened.",
    "Stir in curry roux, then pour in water and soy sauce; bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Return roasted oxtail to the skillet and simmer uncovered for 45 minutes until sauce thickens.",
    "Serve hot over steamed rice."
